      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the math part, but the \"thieves\" thing is a bit weird. can u just stick to the numbers? i'm more confused about how the interest is calculated daily vs monthly. like, how exactly does the daily rate work for my balance?",
      "source": "evaluator"
